o documentation on http://hamsterdb.com/public/scripts/html_www/modules.html:
    hamsterdb Cursor Functions is a child of hamsterdb Database Functions - but
    o the filesize of hamsterdb is HUGE (more than 3 times higher than bdb).
        are these pages part of the freelist? extend ham_info to dump 
